high_descs: Turn to the right and find the table.
Pick up the bread from the edge of the table.
Carry the bread and turn to the right, then the left and face the fridge on the left side.
Open the fridge and place the bread inside. Shut the door, then open it. Take out the bread and shut the door.
Take the bread and move a few steps to the left to find the white table.
Place the bread on the right side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Chill a loaf of bread and move it to the table.

high_descs: Turn right and face the white table with the loaf of bread.
Pick up the loaf of bread.
Walk to the fridge across the room.
Place the loaf of bread in the fridge on the second shelf, let the bread chill for a few seconds, take the bread out of the fridge and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the white table on the right.
Put the bread down on the white table.
anns.task_desc: To chill a loaf of bread and put it on the table.

high_descs: Approach the table on your right.
pick up the bread on the table.
Turn to your right and walk to the fridge.
Place the bread in the fridge, wait, and remove the bread.
Turn to your left and walk to the square table.
place the bread on the square table.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled loaf of bread on the square table.

high_descs: Go forward a step and turn right.
Pick up the loaf of bread.
Go forward and left to the fridge.
Place the bread on the bottom shelf of the fridge, close the fridge, and then open it again and retrieve the bread.
Turn left and walk a few steps to get back to the white table. Face the table.
Place the loaf of bread on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled loaf of bread on a table.

high_descs: Turn right and face the white table.
Pick up the loaf of bread from the table.
Carry the bread over to the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator door and put the bread inside then close the door. Wait 5 seconds then open the door and take the bread out.
Walk back over to the white table.
Put the bread down on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Make the bread on the white table cold.

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the table.
Pick up the loaf of bread from the table.
Turn right, move forward, then turn left and walk to the end of the room, then turn left and face the white refrigerator.

Open the refrigerator and place the bread in the refrigerator on the rack below the lettuce, then close the refrigerator and wait for several minutes, then open the refrigerator and take the bread out.
Turn to the left and walk to the end of the room, then turn right and face the white table.
Put the bread on the table.
anns.task_desc: Cool the loaf of bread in the refrigerator.
